# Use this ONLY if you deploy the frontend on Cloudflare Pages and the API on a *separate* Worker.
# Copy to `frontend/public/_redirects`, set YOUR Worker URL, then build.
# If you use one Worker for UI + API (`cd worker && npm run deploy`), do NOT add `_redirects` ‚Äî see DEPLOY.md.

/api/*  https://YOUR-WORKER-SUBDOMAIN.workers.dev/api/:splat  200
/*     /index.html  200
